
inoremap jj <Esc>

nnoremap <C-a>j <C-w>j
nnoremap <C-a>k <C-w>k
nnoremap <C-a>h <C-w>h
nnoremap <C-a>l <C-w>l

nnoremap <C-a>_ :xcmenucmd Editor<CR>
nnoremap <C-a>_ :xcmenucmd Editor On Right<CR>
nnoremap <C-a>- :xcmenucmd Editor Below<CR>
nnoremap <C-a>x :xcmenucmd Close Editor<CR>
nnoremap <C-a>z :xcmenucmd Focus<CR>
nnoremap <C-a>r :xcmenucmd Change Editor Orientation<CR>

nmap <space>f :xcmenucmd Open Quickly...<CR>
nmap <space>n :nissue<CR>
nmap <space>p :pissue<CR>
nmap <space>i :xcmenucmd Jump to Generated Interface<CR>

nmap <space>g :xcmenucmd History...<CR>
nmap <space>F :xccmd showInFinder<CR>
nmap <space>D :xccmd showDeveloperDocumentation<CR>
nmap <space>d :xcmenucmd Quick Help for Selected Item<CR>

" Toggle Toolbars
nmap <space>h :xccmd toggleNavigatorsVisibility<CR>
nmap <space>j :xccmd toggleDebuggerVisibility<CR>
nmap <space>l :xcmenucmd Hide Inspectors<CR>
nmap <space>l :xcmenucmd Show Inspectors<CR>

nmap <space>b :xcmenucmd Build<CR>
nmap <space>c :%s/^ +$//g<CR> 

noremap <C-a>H :xcmenucmd Go Back<CR>
noremap <C-a>L :xcmenucmd Go Forward<CR>
